Boyz N the Hood;;93;;96;;R;;Tre (Cuba Gooding Jr.) is sent to live with his father, Furious Styles (Larry Fishburne), in tough South Central Los Angeles. Although his hard-nosed father instills proper values and respect in him, and his devout girlfriend Brandi (Nia Long) teaches him about faith, Tre's friends Doughboy (Ice Cube) and Ricky (Morris Chestnut) don't have the same kind of support and are drawn into the neighborhood's booming drug and gang culture, with increasingly tragic results.;;Drama;;John Singleton;;1991;;Laurence Fishburne,Ice Cube,Cuba Gooding Jr.,Nia Long,Morris Chestnut,Tyra Ferrell,Angela Bassett,Meta King,Whitman Mayo,Desi A. Hines II,Baha Jackson,Donovan McCrary;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/boyz_n_the_hood